params.amount: amount of the default collateral to unwrap and deposit
params.collateral: address of the default collateral to unwrap
params.onBehalfOf: address of the account to deposit the underlying asset on behalf of
params.vault: address of the vault to deposit the collateral's underlying asset

returns.depositedAmount: real amount of the collateral deposited
returns.mintedShares: amount of the active shares minted

migrate(address,address,address,uint256).notice: Unwrap a particular default collateral and deposit its underlying asset to a given vault.
